Module nl.naturalis.common

Package nl.naturalis.common.collection

Classes extending the functionality of the Java Collection framework.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    IntList  
    TypeMap<V>
    A Map extension that returns a non-null value for a type if either the type itself or any of its super types is present in the map.
